INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (189601, 'You''re going to come across some truly gifted people in your lifetime that seem to know all the answers. However, they lost their personal relationship with God, along the way. Love them anyways, and do everything you can to help them restore that relationship. They are fighting a war that you don''t know anything about.', 290, 0), (189602, 'But the thing is, I didn''t make my friends happy and they didn''t make me happy. All we did was get stoned out of our minds. That didn''t have anything to do with happiness.', 186, 0), (189603, 'Well, it is very odd of you to threaten to throw your friends out of the window, I must say," remarked Juliana.He smiled. "Not at all. It is only my friends that I would throw out of the window.""Dear me!" said Juliana, finding the male sex incomprehensible.-Chapter XIII', 2209, 0), (189604, 'Friend of everyone is friend of none.', 34629, 0), (189605, 'Some people said beware of enemies. Some said beware of friends and some said beware of frenemies, but the most dangerous people are those that will hurt you and still play the victim.', 34624, 0), (189606, 'You were spying on me?" I repeated, this time my tone was stern."Nonsense! I was making sure you were safe." He answered, fluttering his wings and landing in front of me. "That''s what friends do.', 26405, 0), (189607, 'Her skin hummed with anticipation of Jaxon’s touch. She squeezed her thighs as her womb clenched. This could all go brilliantly or it could all go to hell.', 34630, 0), (189608, 'Some people say beware of enemies. Some say beware of friends and some say beware of frenemies, but the most dangerous people are those that will hurt you and still play the victim.', 34624, 0), (189609, 'the world feel empty without a best friend .true friends no doubt are rare in this world', 34631, 0), (189610, 'If it''s painful for you to criticize your friends, you''re safe in doing it; if you take the slightest pleasure in it, that''s the time to hold your tongue.', 2806, 0), (189611, 'The curve of my waist in a tight fitting summer dress can really make me new friends.', 18376, 0), (189612, 'There are people you wont miss, but wont forget either. Those people are unique', 34632, 0), (189613, 'Finishing a good book is like leaving a good friend', 5249, 0), (189614, ' ''Are we done? You can avoid us all again and we''ll keep talking about you behind your back.'' ', 34633, 0), (189615, 'Now-people” are winners; they say “now” and they do it now! That’s the spirit we need, my friends. If you have the goals and the environment is clear enough, go ahead and do it now!', 3301, 0), (189616, ' ''I''m not that easy to get rid of,'' Andre retorts. ''As you know well. What state are you in? Besides confusion.'' ', 34633, 0), (189617, 'As we were told about others, so others will be told about us. that is "HISTORY". and the most painfull thing about it is that, it does not repeat itself. it comes onece in life and never again.', 26441, 0), (189618, 'Your best friends should bring out the best in you. If they don''t, lose them; they are no friends.', 11230, 0), (189619, 'But friendship meant you at least planted the seed for them, love meant allowing them the ability to weed their own garden until it was something healthy and thriving, blooming and bright and smelling of heather and tiger lilies.', 34634, 0), (189620, 'Harry loves slimy things, hairy things, and creepy things. Harry loves anything horrible. I know -- I''m his best friend Doug.', 34635, 0), (189621, 'Friendship isn''t about becoming somebody else perfect person. It is about finding someone who helps you become the best person you can be.', 32617, 0), (189622, 'You try hard, but you don''t succeed.. So you try harder, and harder... But you still just don''t succeed, you give it a try once more; only realising its never going to work out the way you want it to. But then again, you remember; you''ve tried so much. You''ve tried to